title: Kareshi no Neko ga Kawaikunai!
original_name: 彼氏のネコがかわいくない!
sinopse:
The start of a lovey-dovey life together! Or it should've been, but Matsuri's now living together with her boyfriend's beloved cat Sayuri...?! The struggle for her boyfriend with her cat-in-law begins!

(Source: Seikaisha, translated)
